  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the development of anti-drug antibody to biosimilar
      CT-P13 and to assess the change of drug concentration for 1 year in patients with moderately
      to severe inflammatory bowel disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
